      <title>Le Pen获得了即时的选举禁令；持续时间仍然不知道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-gets-immediate-election-ban-duration-still-not-known</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼的领导人海军勒庞因挪用公司被定罪，并由巴黎法官及其选举禁令；但是他们仍然需要说是否足够长的时间才能将她排除在2027年的法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-gets-immediate-election-ban-duration-still-not-known</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:12:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
