    <item>
      <title>法国的勒庞因滥用欧盟资金而感到内gui</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/france-s-le-pen-found-guilty-in-case-over-misuse-of-eu-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼的领导人海军勒庞（Marine Le Pen）被巴黎法院犯有挪用公款罪名成立，并立即禁止代表选举＆Mdash;但是，法官还没有说是否足够长，可以阻止她跑步，以在2027年成为法国的下一任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/france-s-le-pen-found-guilty-in-case-over-misuse-of-eu-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 09:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本在新财政年度开始的前一天通过了预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japan-to-approve-budget-just-a-day-before-new-fiscal-year-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本议会经过多次修订后通过了初始预算，这减轻了总理史密斯·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）的一些压力，因为他面临许多国内和外交挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japan-to-approve-budget-just-a-day-before-new-fiscal-year-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 04:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
